    <briefdescription>
<para>This is the base class for all the Fields which can be written by a call to Problem::setInputField. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para><verbatim>There are for derived classes for uniform or not / domain or boundary fields.
All are supposed to be time-dependent.

Each Pb_base keeps a list of references to the Champ_Input_Proto it contains.
</verbatim></para>
<para><simplesect kind="see"><para>Champ_Input, Champ_Input_Uniforme, Champ_Front_Input, Champ_Front_Input_Uniforme </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
